This topic explains how to install <%= vars.product_name  %> on Microsoft Azure using Terraform.

To install <%= vars.product_name %> on Azure using Terraform, do the following:

1. Deploy Pivotal Operations Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure Using Terraform](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/azure/prepare-env-terraform.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure Using Terraform](/platform/ops-manager/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.', '-') %>/azure/config-terraform.html).

1. Configure PAS. See [Configuring PAS](./configure-pas.html).
